  "texts": [
    "In total, we retrieved 344,411 individually disclosed literacy components from 6,986 executives between July and September 2022.",
    "The executives belonged to 645 different firms, thereof 477 incumbent firms and 168 startup firms.",
    "We used information disclosed by the firms on LinkedIn.",
    "com and official annual reports (10-K statement) to collect the additional necessary firm data.",
    "On LinkedIn.com, firms can publish job postings and share firm-related information as posts (robustness check for sample selection bias see Appendix B.3)."
  ],
